what_worked: Applied early_filter, pushdown, materialize_cte: Isolated date filtering into a CTE to push down to the fact table join early, converted implicit joins to explicit joins for optimizer clarity, and simplified the CASE expression in the main filter since `avg_monthly_sales > 0` is already guaranteed.
why_it_worked: Applying selective filters early reduces intermediate row counts before expensive operations; Pushing predicates closer to table scans reduces data volume in upper operators; Materializing a CTE used multiple times prevents redundant re-computation
